    <articleTitle>
      <Value><![CDATA[Irradiation with 780 nm diode laser attenuates inflammatory cytokines but upregulates nitric oxide in lipo-polysaccharide-stimulated macrophages: implications for the prevention of aneurysm progression.]]></Value>
